<title>
Differential Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206010">Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206015">Manual Transaxle Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206028">Differential Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5206029001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Support differential case with soft jawed vise and remove final gear bolts, and then remove final gear.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove left bearing (2) using bearing puller (1) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520061.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.931mm" ver = "01" gw = "160" gh = "145"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove right bearing (1) using special tools.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B040">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-65135">
09913–65135
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B041">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85230">
09913–85230
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520077.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "49.646mm" ver = "01" gw = "115" gh = "124"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove differential pinion shaft (3) pin using special tool and hammer and then disassemble component parts.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B042">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-85811">
09922–85811
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A520046.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.106mm" ver = "01" gw = "107" gh = "117"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
