<s1>
<ptxt>
Hold differential assembly with soft jawed vise (3), install final gear (2) and then tighten new final gear bolts (1) to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<attention4>
<ptxt>
The bolts may loosen during operation of the differential if any bolts other than the specified bolts are installed.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Use only the specified bolts.
</ptxt>
</attention4>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5B014">
<t-part>
Final gear bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
90
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
9.2
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
66.5
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
